{"tid":2182823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心apple咪用SF送啦","createTime":"2020-08-31T14:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T15:13:58.000Z","uid":371991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51ca095d7ca990fca83c1fa1211eaed6334ac6bc","tid":2182823,"uid":371991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"8月21用大專優惠買Macbook ，到今日8月31顯示會派到貨<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRoBG7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRoBG7s.png&h=9353b2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去返順豐度睇下午12點已經派送緊 ，等到下午5點打比送件員電話飛哂去留言，再打去sf客服又係線路繁忙直接cut左電話。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94gr4jp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94gr4jp.png&h=14e256d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到7點幾打去sf客服投訴電話就話9點前送到，結果9點07分先話聯絡唔到我取消派送。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mN3ia08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmN3ia08.png&h=5a7d75b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日打左5、6個電話比條友都唔聽，客服又唔聽，去到9點先話取消，唔係apple優惠要網上訂又冇得簡速遞公司，真係唔會用垃圾sf🤮🤮次次都唔同時間送，要個客等你成日仲可以自己cut單。"},{"pid":"3e6085d43331b05131fc1920adf8786db927e35d","tid":2182823,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aaa87ad975daf3f3dbbe8a1fb9b275ca563ba96e","tid":2182823,"uid":111812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"有時蘋果用宅急便，啲服務仲衰"},{"pid":"602ccfac0191ebd9eea37bd5fd2664db770c7e46","tid":2182823,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"廣東話-&gt;投訴"},{"pid":"d23a4380683c80d5b97be06b671c5def0f15c4c9","tid":2182823,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e6085d43331b05131fc1920adf8786db927e35d","tid":2182823,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:26:34.000Z","m